  "bodyHtml": "<span style=\"font-family: Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\">Phonecheck now supports Apple Watch data collection and erasure. In this article, we’ll teach you how to do it.<br><br>Hardware requirements: </span>\n<ul><li><span style=\"font-family: Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\"><strong><a href=\"https://fr.aliexpress.com/item/1005003302088737.html?spm=a2g0o.productlist.main.9.7770NtUaNtUam7&amp;algo_pvid=0cfd5cfe-8f5d-4c1a-b4e7-185d3346fee1&amp;aem_p4p_detail=202311100054201472606518090400003240196&amp;algo_exp_id=0cfd5cfe-8f5d-4c1a-b4e7-185d3346fee1-4&amp;pdp_npi=4%40dis%21EUR%21121.89%21119.45%21%21%21127.03%21%21%40211b61bb16996064604777390e8b7a%2112000025100489966%21sea%21IT%210%21AB&amp;curPageLogUid=4DMVsuuINPHc&amp;search_p4p_id=202311100054201472606518090400003240196_1\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: #3498db;\">All-in-one iBUS tool</span></a></strong> to connect the Apple Watch to Phonecheck</span></li><li><span style=\"font-family: Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\">Lightning cable</span></li><li><span style=\"font-family: Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\">Phonecheck station</span></li></ul>\n<br><span style=\"font-family: Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\"><img alt=\"1.png\" src=\"/ssc/servlet/rtaImage?eid=ka0Sb00000006qD&amp;feoid=00N3X00000M5fJO&amp;refid=0EMSb000000IRxp\" style=\"width: 654px;height: 482px;\"></img><br><br>Software requirements:<br>Apple Watch erasure is available for Mac only at this time (1.3.662.3). Apple Watch data collection is available for Mac and Windows.<br><br>Here are a few tips:</span>\n\n<ul><li><span style=\"font-family: Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\">Apple Watch erasure on Windows will be added at a later date</span></li><li><span style=\"font-family: Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\">Apple Watch erasure is user-guided</span></li><li><span style=\"font-family: Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\">Apple Watch series 1, 2, 3, 4, 5, and series SE <strong>are</strong> supported</span></li><li><span style=\"font-family: Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\">Apple Watch series 6, 7, 8, SE2, and Ultra <strong>aren’t</strong> supported</span></li></ul>\n<br><span style=\"font-family: Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\">Apple Watch data collection includes:</span>\n\n<ul><li><span style=\"font-family: Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\">Make</span></li><li><span style=\"font-family: Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\">Model</span></li><li><span style=\"font-family: Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\">Model number</span></li><li><span style=\"font-family: Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\">Regulatory model number</span></li><li><span style=\"font-family: Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\">Serial, storage</span></li><li><span style=\"font-family: Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\">Color, software version</span></li><li><span style=\"font-family: Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\">FMI status</span></li><li><span style=\"font-family: Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\">Jailbreak </span></li><li><span style=\"font-family: Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\">Battery metrics</span></li></ul>\n<br><span style=\"font-family: Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\"><img alt=\"2.png\" src=\"/ssc/servlet/rtaImage?eid=ka0Sb00000006qD&amp;feoid=00N3X00000M5fJO&amp;refid=0EMSb000000ISFZ\" style=\"width: 339px;height: 577px;\"></img><img alt=\"3.png\" src=\"/ssc/servlet/rtaImage?eid=ka0Sb00000006qD&amp;feoid=00N3X00000M5fJO&amp;refid=0EMSb000000ISIn\" style=\"width: 339px;height: 577px;\"></img><br><br><br>This will help you quickly know if an Apple Watch is iCloud locked and its battery health with <strong>no need to activate or synch it with an iPhone</strong>.<br><br>Here’s how you do this:</span>\n\n<ol><li><span style=\"font-family: Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\">Remove the cap protecting the connector (only available in series 1, 2, 3, 4, 5, and Series SE) with tweezers.</span></li><li><span style=\"font-family: Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\">Connect the Apple Watch to the <a href=\"https://fr.aliexpress.com/item/1005003302088737.html?spm=a2g0o.productlist.main.9.7770NtUaNtUam7&amp;algo_pvid=0cfd5cfe-8f5d-4c1a-b4e7-185d3346fee1&amp;aem_p4p_detail=202311100054201472606518090400003240196&amp;algo_exp_id=0cfd5cfe-8f5d-4c1a-b4e7-185d3346fee1-4&amp;pdp_npi=4%40dis%21EUR%21121.89%21119.45%21%21%21127.03%21%21%40211b61bb16996064604777390e8b7a%2112000025100489966%21sea%21IT%210%21AB&amp;curPageLogUid=4DMVsuuINPHc&amp;search_p4p_id=202311100054201472606518090400003240196_1\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: #3498db;\"><strong>all-in-one iBUS tool</strong></span></a>.</span></li><li><span style=\"font-family: Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\">The Apple Watch will show up on Phonecheck.</span></li><li><span style=\"font-family: Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\">Information will show up automatically.</span></li><li><span style=\"font-family: Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\">Report will be available in your console.</span></li></ol>\n<br><img alt=\"4.png\" src=\"/ssc/servlet/rtaImage?eid=ka0Sb00000006qD&amp;feoid=00N3X00000M5fJO&amp;refid=0EMSb000000ISdl\"></img><br> "
}